{"comments":"Video Broadcast Color Atoms and Molecules.\n\n**VIDEO COLOR ENCODING STANDARDS:**\nVideo color spaces separate luminance (Y) from chrominance for\nefficient transmission and backward compatibility with B&W systems.\n\n**Atoms:**\n- `Luma` - Y luminance component (0.0-1.0), already in YUV.purs\n- `Cb` - Blue-difference chroma (-0.5 to +0.5)\n- `Cr` - Red-difference chroma (-0.5 to +0.5)\n- `I` - In-phase NTSC chroma (-0.5 to +0.5)\n- `Q` - Quadrature NTSC chroma (-0.5 to +0.5)\n\n**Molecules:**\n- `YCbCr` - Digital video (ITU-R BT.601/709)\n- `YIQ` - NTSC analog (North America)\n- `YPbPr` - Component analog video\n\n**Why multiple standards?**\n- YUV/YPbPr: Analog component video (PAL, SECAM)\n- YCbCr: Digital video (JPEG, MPEG, H.264, web video)\n- YIQ: NTSC broadcast (legacy North America)\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Video"],"Cb"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[121,30],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Video.purs","start":[121,1]},"title":"eqCb"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Ord"],"Ord"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Video"],"Cb"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[122,32],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Video.purs","start":[122,1]},"title":"ordCb"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Video"],"Cb"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[125,32],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Video.purs","start":[124,1]},"title":"showCb"}],"comments":"Cb - Blue-difference chroma (-0.5 to +0.5)\n\nComponent of YCbCr digital video. Represents the difference between\nblue and luminance: Cb = (B - Y) / 1.772\n","info":{"dataDeclType":"newtype","declType":"data","roles":[],"typeArguments":[]},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[119,23],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Video.purs","start":[119,1]},"title":"Cb"},{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Video"],"Cr"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[143,30],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Video.purs","start":[143,1]},"title":"eqCr"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Ord"],"Ord"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Video"],"Cr"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[144,32],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Video.purs","start":[144,1]},"title":"ordCr"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Show"],"Show"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","Video"],"Cr"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"sourceSpan":{"end":[147,32],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Color/Video.purs","start":[146,1]},"title":"showCr"}],"comments":"Cr - Red-difference chroma (-0.5 to +0.5)\n\nComponent of YCbCr digital video. Represents the difference between\nred and luminance: Cr = (R - Y) / 1.402\n","info":{"dataDeclType":"newtype","declType":"data","roles":[],"typeArgument